#: ../../ddns.rst:6 66bcb693cf2644a3b37bcbb3ac47ca92
msgid ""
"Dynamic DNS (DDNS) automatically updates your domain name's DNS record "
"with your current IP address, even if it changes dynamically. This allows"
" you to access your firewall remotely using a consistent domain name "
"instead of remembering a potentially changing IP address."
msgstr ""

